<para id="fs-id1167661743336">For a transplant to have the best chances of avoiding rejection, the genes coding for the ________ molecules should be closely matched between donor and recipient.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167661645545">
<para id="fs-id1167663740492">MHC</para>
</solution>
