<problem id="fs-id1167663544564">
<para id="fs-id1167663742772">Because it is a “transplant” that can include APCs and T cells from the donor, a bone marrow transplant may induce a very specific type of rejection known as ________ disease.</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-id1167661288470">
<para id="fs-id1167663670135">graft-versus-host</para>
